<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to ShopEase</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 30px 15px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #ffffff;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #4f46e5);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
      position: relative;
    }
    .header::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fbbf24, #f59e0b, #fbbf24);
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    .welcome-badge {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #111827;
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .text {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #2563eb;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .features {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 15px;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .feature-item:hover {
      transform: translateX(5px);
      background: #f3f4f6;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #4f46e5);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-right: 15px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .feature-text h3 {
      margin: 0 0 5px 0;
      color: #111827;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .feature-text p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .cta-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 25px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 15px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #4f46e5);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
    }
    .promo-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24, #f59e0b);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .promo-banner h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .promo-banner p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .promo-code {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      border: 2px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #e5e7eb, transparent);
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .social-links {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .social-links a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .social-links a:hover {
      color: #2563eb;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f9fafb;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #2563eb;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
      }
      .btn {
        padding: 12px 24px;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <h1>🎉 Welcome to ShopEase!</h1>
        <p>Your smart online shopping destination</p>
        <div class="welcome-badge">✨ New Member</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
        
        <p class="text">
          We're thrilled to have you join the <span class="highlight">ShopEase family</span>! 
          You've just unlocked access to thousands of products, exclusive deals, and a shopping 
          experience designed with you in mind.
        </p>

        <p class="text">
          Your journey to smarter shopping starts now. Whether you're looking for the latest trends, 
          everyday essentials, or special gifts, we've got you covered with unbeatable prices and 
          lightning-fast delivery.
        </p>


        <!-- Features -->



        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="cta-section">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #111827;">Ready to Start Shopping?</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #4b5563;">
            Browse our newest arrivals and trending products today!
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="btn">Start Shopping Now →</a>
        </div>

        <p class="text" style="margin-top: 30px;">
          Need help getting started? Our friendly customer support team is available 24/7 to assist you. 
          Simply reply to this email or visit our <a href="#" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">Help Center</a>.
        </p>

        <p class="text" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
          Happy shopping!<br/>
          <strong style="color: #2563eb;">The ShopEase Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Social Links -->
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="#">Facebook</a> • 
        <a href="#">Instagram</a> • 
        <a href="#">Twitter</a> • 
        <a href="#">Pinterest</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        © 2026 ShopEase. All rights reserved.<br/>
        Made with ❤️ for a better shopping experience.<br/><br/>
        <a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Service</a><br/>
        123 Commerce Street, Shopping District, Your City, 12345
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>